
------------------------------------
| Battletech Mech-Konstruktor V1.0 |
------------------------------------



Systemrequirements:

The programm "Mech-Konstruktor" should run on every AMIGA-System. But if
you have an AGA-AMIGA or one with a graphic-card you can also see a title.



Installation:

For the best you should copy the directory "Battletech" on harddisk.
But it is important to beware the structure of the sub-directories.
The structure have to be like this:

Battletech
|
|-Erstelle_Assigns (Skript)
|
|-Bilder
| |
| |-Mechs
| |
| |-Sonstiges
|
|-Dokumentation
|
|-Editoren_für_Einheiten
| 
|-Einheiten
| |
| |-Mechs
|   |
|   |-Leichte
|   |
|   |-Mittelschwere
|   |
|   |-Schwere
|   |
|   |-Überschwere
|
|-Einstellungen
|
|-Konfiguration 



Before you start the program, you have to execute the script 
"Erstelle_Assigns". At the moment the software needs three assigns:

Battletech:
BattleBilder:
BattleEinheiten:

If you want, you can also insert the assigns in your user-startup.

For example if you want to install "Battletech" in the directory
work:games the assigns have to look like this:

Assign Battletech: Work:Spiele/Battletech
Assign BattleBilder: Work:Spiele/BattleBilder
Assign BattleEinheiten: Work:Spiele/Battletech



Theoretically you can run the program also from disk.
For this you need three disks with the following names:

Battletech
BattleBilder
BattleEinheiten

The directory-structure have to look like this. Copy the files in the
directories and look for my declarations.



Battletech
|
|-Bilder
| |
| |-Sonstiges (copy only "_kein_Bild" in this directory)
|
|-Dokumentation
|
|-Editoren_für_Einheiten
| 
|-Einstellungen
|
|-Konfiguration 



BattleBilder
|
|-Bilder
  |
  |-Sonstiges (copy only "Mech-Konstruktor_Titel" in this directory)



BattleEinheiten
|
|-Bilder
| |
| |-Mechs
|
|-Einheiten
  |
  |-Mechs
    |
    |-Leichte
    |
    |-Mittelschwere
    |
    |-Schwere
    |
    |-Überschwere



